data.text: 167 students and staff from the Alexander Moss High School in Israel departed on the nonstop Miami flight to #Israel. Thank you for flying #ELAL, we hope you come back and see us soon! https://t.co/iSSfHWwDQ4

Do you like to snack on your flights? #ELAL Premium Class passengers can choose from a rich menu full of tasty treats to enjoy throughout the ride. What are your favorite plane snacks? https://t.co/ss8Sn0y3E1
Craving couscous? Try your hand at this classic Mediterranean dish. @joyofkosher https://t.co/llCcTw8IIg https://t.co/OPHjcI46JK

The First Station complex is the center of entertainment, culture, and more in #Jerusalem. The outdoor mall has everything from live events to kid-friendly activities perfect for the entire family. What's your favorite thing to do at First Station?
📸 Udi Goren https://t.co/QpkJwEU5nR

Prepare to be pampered! #ELAL is partnering with @Brown_Hotels to provide complementary Brown Spa services in the EL AL King David Lounge at the Ben Gurion International Airport. The spa is open Sunday-Thursday, from 4pm-12am. Make a reservation here: https://t.co/lD8Hfx4NV4 https://t.co/MELXelYa5G
